title: Ep. 397 - Babita Does The Bating - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita finally enters the field to do the bating. The Daya team was playing far well and it motivated them. Then when it was Jethalal's time to do the bating, it was Daya who was bowling for him. But Jethalal did lose to Daya in the match.

title: Ep. 398 - Roles Reverse In The Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Now Daya teams do the batting and Babita's team does the Feilding. As the roles are reversed, the match gets a little more interesting. And it got a lot funnier when Popatlal was batting.

title: Ep. 399 - Parthiv Patel Reviews The GPL Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A little break in GPL 2 match, where they conducted a Dandiya dance performance. A nail-biting experience in the match where the Daya team has to move forward to get wickets to win the match. An international cricketer Parthiv reviews the GPL match.

title: Ep. 400 - Captain Daya Enters The Feild For Bating - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The GPL 2 match has entered the last phase, where Daya enters the field to do batting. But ends up being mocked by her wig. The last ball decides the fate of the GPL 2 match. Which team will win the match?

title: Ep. 401 - The Last Ball  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The GPL 2 match has come to an end. The last ball is thrown! Did Daya score her wicket to win the match? or Not? This is the phase where there will be a lot of rewinds to give acute attention to the details of the last ball.

title: Ep. 402 - Daya Dandiya Devil Team Wins The GPL 2 Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The GPL 2 match concluded with the Daya team winning the match and Sodhi winning the title, 'Man of the Match'. Hence both the team concludes the match with perfect understanding and all the issues that we are on the match, resolved peacefully.

title: Ep. 403 - Silence After The Storm - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Silence prevails after all the loud cheers for the Gokuldam Premier League 2 match. Back to their normal lives, with the memories to savor from the match. But Bhide being the secretary, is aware of his responsibilities.

title: Ep. 404 - Tapu Learns A Life Lesson - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal's mobile was stuck on the sofa when his dad tried to take it his hand was stuck on the sofa. So they had to call Sodhi for help. Jethala got his mobile back, but his sofa needs to be repaired.

title: Ep. 405 - Champaklal Loses His Money Bag - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal decides to help the boy who struggles to pay his school fees, so Tapu and his friends decide to help him along with his grandfather, while Jethala also helps him. But on the way to school through taxi, Champaklal loses his money bag.

title: Ep. 406 - Man Of The Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi goes to Rita, the reporter to get a copy of the GPL 2 match telecast in CD. He was so excited to watch him and others play. He was on cloud nine when he heard the other cricketers' comments about him when he won the man of the match.

title: Ep. 407 - Sodhi Leaves Without Informing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi's had a dream about GPL 2 match and was so into meeting the actual cricketers. So in the very morning, Sodhi shows his gratitude to Daya for being her captain. And leaves to meet the cricketer without informing his wife and son.

title: Ep. 408 - Sodhi's Dream Come True - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: He finally got his chance to meet the India team cricketers. But there was tension brimming in Sodhi's family and the whole society came forward to help. Finally, when Sodhi contacted them, they were relieved and he came back home happy.

title: Ep. 409 - Jethalal's Childhood Photos - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Anjali appreciates Tappu and his friends for helping with donations for the student to pay his school tuition fees. Champaklal was busy fixing his old suitcase, where Tappu discover few old photos of Jethalal.

title: Ep. 410 - Jethalal Helps Babita - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita seeks Jethalal's help to get her mobile phone fixed. But Jethala gets a headache, where Daya helps him with giving massages. But that doesn't seem to work with the only headache. Rather he ends having spiky hair.

title: Ep. 411 - Jethalal's Weird Hairstyle - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal's hair gets into a very bad shape after he applies the shampoo which Sunder has sent.  In the meantime, Iyer and Babita visit Jethalal and Iyer wants to try the shampoo which Jethalal has used. Iyer is not aware of his upcoming trouble.
